wikipedia_page.main: Charles O'Sullivan, DD (b Ballyfinnane 22 August 1858; d Killarney 29 January 1927) was an Irish Roman Catholic Bishop in the first third of the 20th century.O'Sullivan was educated at St Patrick's College, Maynooth and ordained in 1884. He was Bishop of Ardfert and Aghadoe from 1917 until his death.
